{"tid":1524363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【關稅已加】特朗普：新一輪對華關稅 9月1日準時實施","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T06:05:02.000Z","uid":33307,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"245fc2e052d5a1b91f833975c9d00b85218c7212","tid":1524363,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:05:08.000Z","msg":"中美貿易戰持續，美國對中國貨品加新一輪關稅期限將至，美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）表示，關稅會如期於9月1日實施，並強調關稅對美國經濟不構成影響。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在白宮向記者表示，有企業將問題歸因關稅，但其實這些公司經營得很差，是自身管理不善，用關稅作籍口。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普並在twitter發帖文，重申美國沒有關稅問題，反有聯儲局問題，形容聯儲局對事情一無所知。<br />\n<br />\n他並向通用汽車（General Motors）施壓，促集團將車廠搬回美國，指通用汽車曾是底特律最大車廠，現在變成最小。<br />\n<br />\n美國將於當地時間周日凌晨開始，對總值約1250億美元中國貨品加徵15%關稅，包括智能手錶、平面電視機及鞋等。<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，中國亦採取相應關稅報復，對750億美元美國貨加徵5%關稅，同樣於9月1日實施。"},{"pid":"6f5694cba2792d61f5082ab3c9e0efd229d8a751","tid":1524363,"uid":138609,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:06:40.000Z","msg":"唯一正面新聞<br />\n侵侵一定要打沉支那共產黨<br />\n世界毒瘤"},{"pid":"eff241048a196c34f6a533bd35fa2ba6599c9e02","tid":1524363,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:06:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721/831無獎問答遊戲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H8DUzH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH8DUzH7.jpg&h=4b81709e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lxqsagt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxqsagt.jpg&h=281798cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">試辨認以上事件發生日子</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">都一樣，係無差別攻擊！</span></span>"},{"pid":"84cf0ce5e180c50c05dcb3ae6cb84d77ff012ec6","tid":1524363,"uid":33307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime